Package it.unipd.dei.se.parse

package it.unipd.dei.se.parse
This package contains examples complementing the lectures of the Search Engines course.

Search Engines is a course of the

  • Master Degree in Computer Engineering of the Department of Information Engineering;
  • Master Degree in Data Science of the Department of Mathematics "Tullio Levi-Civita";

both at University of Padua, Italy.

Search Engines is part of the teaching activities of the Intelligent Interactive Information Access (IIIA) Hub.
